  - **Step 2:** Choose Your Stay - Browse through listings and select the one that fits your needs.
  - **Step 3:** Book with Confidence - Secure your booking with our easy-to-use platform.
  - **Step 4:** Enjoy Your Stay - Have an amazing experience with RoamStay.

